  "page": "Feature quote/234",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div style=\"font-style:italic;padding-left:1em;display:flow-root;\" class=\"poem\">\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Tyrion_Lannister\" title=\"Tyrion Lannister\">He</a> rode through the streets of <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">the city</a>,<br />\n<span class=\"mw-poem-indented\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin-left: 1em;\">down from <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Keep\" title=\"Red Keep\">his hill on high</a>,</span><br />\nO'er the wynds and the steps and the cobbles,<br />\n<span class=\"mw-poem-indented\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin-left: 1em;\">he rode to <a href=\"/index.php/Shae\" title=\"Shae\">a woman</a>'s sigh.</span><br />\nFor she was his secret treasure,<br />\n<span class=\"mw-poem-indented\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin-left: 1em;\">she was his shame and his bliss. </span><br />\nAnd a <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">chain</a> and a keep are nothing,<br />\n<span class=\"mw-poem-indented\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin-left: 1em;\">compared to a woman's kiss.</span><br />\nFor hands of gold are cold, but a woman's hands are warm...\n</p>\n</div><p> —<a href=\"/index.php/Symon_Silver_Tongue\" title=\"Symon Silver Tongue\">Symon Silver Tongue</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos32.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_32\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 32\">Chapter 32</a>, Tyrion IV.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404093333\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.008 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.009 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 98/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8476/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 370/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 443/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 1/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1596/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    5.333      1 -total\n 70.50%    3.760      1 Template:Ref\n 49.39%    2.634      1 Template:Ref/core\n 28.41%    1.515      1 Template:Lyrics\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:26679-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404093333 and revision id 244096\n -->\n",
